ZH: 1. 发展经济是国家的首要任务。
EN: Developing the economy is the country's top priority.

ZH: 2. 企业需要不断创新才能取得良好的发展。
EN: Companies need to innovate continuously in order to achieve good development.

ZH: 3. 教育是人才的重要来源，对社会发展至关重要。
EN: Education is an important source of talent and critical to social development.

ZH: 4. 人与自然的和谐发展是可持续发展的关键之一。
EN: The harmonious development between humans and nature is one of the keys to sustainable development.

ZH: 5. 国际合作是推动全球经济发展的重要手段。
EN: International cooperation is an important means to drive global economic development.

ZH: 6. 创业是年轻人一种实现自身发展的途径。
EN: Entrepreneurship is a way for young people to achieve personal development.

ZH: 7. 技术的不断进步促进了社会的发展。
EN: The continuous advancement of technology promotes societal development.

ZH: 8. 发展一定要有可持续性，不能只顾眼前利益。
EN: Development must be sustainable and not just focused on short-term gains.

ZH: 9. 文化是一个国家软实力和发展的重要依托。
EN: Culture is an important foundation for a country's soft power and development.

ZH: 10. 医疗卫生事业的发展关系到人民的健康和生活质量。
EN: The development of healthcare is related to the health and quality of life of the people.

ZH: 11. 交通设施的发展对城市的发展起着至关重要的作用。
EN: The development of transportation facilities plays a critical role in urban development.

ZH: 12. 风险管理是企业发展中必不可少的一环。
EN: Risk management is an essential part of business development.

ZH: 13. 政府要制定有效政策来促进经济的稳定发展。
EN: The government needs to formulate effective policies to promote stable economic development.

ZH: 14. 希望通过教育改革来促进教育事业的发展。
EN: We hope to promote the development of education through education reform.

ZH: 15. 让每个人都能参与到社会进步和发展中来是一个国家的责任。
EN: It is a country's responsibility to ensure that everyone can participate in social progress and development.

ZH: 16. 科研成果的转化是推动科技发展和产业升级的关键。
EN: Transforming research results is key to driving technological development and industrial upgrading.

ZH: 17. 环境保护和经济发展应该相辅相成。
EN: Environmental protection and economic development should complement each other.

ZH: 18. 健康是一切幸福的基石，所以要注重健康事业的发展。
EN: Health is the cornerstone of all happiness, so we must pay attention to the development of healthcare.

ZH: 19. 要推动农业现代化是实现乡村振兴和农民增收的重要途径。
EN: Promoting agricultural modernization is an important way to achieve rural revitalization and increase farmers' incomes.

ZH: 20. 政府的角色是推动社会各条线公平而有序的发展。
EN: The government plays a role in promoting fair and orderly development in all aspects of society.
